{
  "stem": "20711.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was not everything was just missing, but I never saw debris at least this high around every home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was not one single window, there was not one door on the house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And all that debris-- it was amazing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My father went over to a neighbor and borrowed some shovels, and we had to shovel ourselves out through the window.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We threw out all the dirt and everything we find on the floor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we decided to concentrate on one room, one of the warmest, inner room, not one of the city, on the street side.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And some neighbors came over to help with his tools, and they boarded up the window, and they made a makeshift door.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And once the room was clean, we got some fresh hay from a neighbor, and we covered the floor with hay, and that's where we slept the first night.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But by the evening, my grandmother came back, who was hiding in the next town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "She was hiding from the Russians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and my beautiful aunts, they were-- all had to hide from the-- the soldiers So when they heard that we are back, they came, and we all slept in that one room, eventually, it was 11 of us.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember that first night, nobody cried but laughed our head off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never remember so much giggling and laughing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We thought it was so funny, from all the money that we used to had, and now, we are sleeping on the hay but every one of us together.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a beautiful occasion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't cried about lost things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were all healthy and together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then little by little, the next day and so, people started to return our thing, voluntary.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
